title: BREAKING: Police say 2 bodies found in Moncrief area on Saturday
content: The Jacksonville Sheriff’s Office found two bodies Saturday in the Moncrief area.    JSO reported an undetermined death in the area of West 31st Street and Stuart Street, as well as another body found in 13th and Moncrief Road.    So far no information regarding those two people has been released to the media.    Stay with First Coast News as we continue to follow this developing story.    © 2018 WTLV
